&lt;p&gt;Data source: &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.gov.uk/government/statistics/police-powers-and-procedures-england-and-wales-year-ending-31-march-2019&#34;&gt;Home Office, 2019&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
